The paper involves the use of deep learning for rib detection and centerline extraction from CT volumes, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper focuses on medical imaging (cs.MS) and specifically on musculoskeletal imaging (cs.MM), which further supports these sub-categories.
